<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<title>HakimCodez | Policy</title>
<%- include('partials/font') %>
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="assets/style.css">
	<style>
		p,h1{
			padding: 0;
			margin: 0;
		}
		h1 + p{
			line-height: 25px;
			text-align: justify;
		}
		h1{
			margin-top: 30px;
			margin-bottom: 12px;
		}
		.container{
			margin: 0 auto;
			max-width: 500px;
			padding: 0 60px;
			padding-top: 60px;
		}
		.container2{
			margin: 0 auto;
			max-width: 500px;
			padding: 0 60px;
			padding-top: 20px;
		}
		.container2 li{
			line-height: 25px;
		}
		.container2 ol ul li:last-child{
			padding-bottom: 30px;
		}
		.container2 ol > li{
			font-weight: bold;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="container2">
	<h1>Policy</h1>
	<ol style="padding-left: 20px;">
		<li>Responsible Use</li>
		<ul>
			<li>This chat app is designed for private and friendly interactions.</li>
			<li>Users must not send messages that are offensive, discriminatory, political, or target religion or individuals.</li>
			<li>Content with sexual, explicit, or inappropriate material is strictly prohibited.</li>
		</ul>
		<li>Privacy</li>
		<ul>
			<li>Conversations are private. Do not share personal sensitive information.</li>
			<li>The app does not store chat content permanently beyond what is necessary for real-time messaging.</li>
		</ul>
		<li>User Responsibility</li>
		<ul>
			<li>Users are responsible for the messages they send.</li>
			<li>Misuse of the platform may result in restricted access or removal.</li>
		</ul>
		<li>Respect and Safety</li>
		<ul>
			<li>Maintain respectful and safe communication at all times.</li>
			<li>Avoid harassment, bullying, or harmful behavior.</li>
		</ul>
		<li>Updates</li>
		<ul>
			<li>This policy may be updated periodically.</li>
			<li>Users should review the policy regularly to stay informed of any changes.</li>
		</ul>
	</ol>
</div>
</body>
</html>